{"tid":2377742,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國軍機於過去2小時5次入侵台灣防空識別區 疑似針對有美軍航空母艦戰鬥群靠近 台灣空軍升空警戒","createTime":"2021-01-24T01:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T02:55:58.000Z","uid":292499,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7c0f9b1b078851f5d655225d9f25d17bd52a2d","tid":2377742,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T01:10:22.000Z","msg":"解放軍軍機密集襲擾我國鄰近空域成常態，昨天早上極罕見在短短2小時內侵入空域達7次，沒想到今天變本加厲，早上7時至今已經5度進入我西南空域，連續密集的襲擾，連長期紀錄的軍事迷都感到相當異常，也辛苦全台空軍疲於應對。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n根據廣播記錄，中共軍機今天上午7時9分、7時45分、8時08分、8時20分、8時28分，連續五度襲擾我西南空域ADIZ，高度分別在6000至9000公尺，我空軍在空警戒，並五度廣播驅離。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3420502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3420502&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2Tarnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=22c68c0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3420502&h=a7bb89f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3420502</a>"},{"pid":"062521c40b5dd6856c0ad3355120dc9461dc9b2e","tid":2377742,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T01:11:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢2日咁密<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f99c1745750d300a2346a7a9f6c8c535de3679c","tid":2377742,"uid":173945,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T01:13:36.000Z","msg":"習：登仔交下戲啦，我就快打柒台灣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bee11e0d9d7849ec08817144f7be937e97a7e97","tid":2377742,"uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f99c1745750d300a2346a7a9f6c8c535de3679c","tid":2377742,"uid":173945,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T01:13:36.000Z","msg":"習：登仔交下戲啦，我就快打柒台灣啦<img src=\"/asset